remarks.summary: All-day strike at 14 transport companies in Brandenburg
remarks.text: The strike at the BVG in Berlin is over. 14 transport companies in Brandenburg will be on strike all day until Saturday, 3:00 a.m.. Trams, buses and ferrys are affected. Long-distance and regional trains as well as S-Bahn trains will run as scheduled. Info: www.vbb.de/streik and www.bvg.de
